WEBVTT

1
00:00:16.317 --> 00:00:17.483
<i>Counterattack!</i>

2
00:00:17.652 --> 00:00:19.878
<i>With the clone army stretched
in a desperate attempt</i>

3
00:00:20.003 --> 00:00:22.191
<i>to engage
General Grievous' starfleet.</i>

4
00:00:22.316 --> 00:00:24.576
<i>Separatist planets
that were once thought secure</i>

5
00:00:24.701 --> 00:00:27.201
<i>are now rising up
against the Republic.</i>

6
00:00:27.440 --> 00:00:30.443
<i>On Geonosis.
Separatist leader Poggle the Lesser.</i>

7
00:00:30.749 --> 00:00:33.109
<i>safe in his newly
ray-shielded factories.</i>

8
00:00:33.234 --> 00:00:35.433
<i>creates thousands
of terrible new weapons</i>

9
00:00:35.558 --> 00:00:39.558
<i>which march off the assembly line
against the outnumbered clone army.</i>

10
00:00:39.956 --> 00:00:43.856
<i>The Jedi. resolute in their effort
to restore order to the Republic</i>

11
00:00:44.211 --> 00:00:46.911
<i>mount a massive invasion
to retake Geonosis</i>

12
00:00:47.272 --> 00:00:49.665
<i>and shut down
Poggle's factories of terror</i>

13
00:00:49.790 --> 00:00:51.140
<i>once and for all.</i>

14
00:00:53.178 --> 00:00:55.678
I cannot believe
we're back here again.

15
00:00:55.991 --> 00:00:57.391
It is unfortunate.

16
00:00:57.655 --> 00:00:59.516
The resistance
from the native Geonosians

17
00:00:59.641 --> 00:01:01.429
was stronger than we anticipated.

18
00:01:01.554 --> 00:01:04.490
The same can be said
for their loyalty to Count Dooku.

19
00:01:04.615 --> 00:01:06.715
A fact that is often overlooked.

20
00:01:06.926 --> 00:01:08.026
You're late.

21
00:01:08.304 --> 00:01:09.304
Sorry. Master.

22
00:01:09.429 --> 00:01:12.038
Ahsoka and I were busy
routing the seppies near Dorin.

23
00:01:12.369 --> 00:01:15.037
My squadron alone had 55 kills.

24
00:01:15.502 --> 00:01:18.062
Yeah. but mine had 76.

25
00:01:18.421 --> 00:01:19.421
Show-off.

26
00:01:19.653 --> 00:01:21.864
I'm glad
you two are enjoying yourselves.

27
00:01:21.989 --> 00:01:24.317
It's just a little
friendly competion. Master.

28
00:01:24.442 --> 00:01:25.718
Nothing to worry about.

29
00:01:25.886 --> 00:01:29.140
What I worry about is the way
this war seems to be drawing out

30
00:01:29.265 --> 00:01:31.010
with no end in sight.

31
00:01:31.267 --> 00:01:35.271
Which is why it is crucial our invasion
of Geonosis meets with success.

32
00:01:35.480 --> 00:01:36.480
Agreed.

33
00:01:37.003 --> 00:01:39.816
Contact the Outer Rim command.
We're ready for our briefing.

34
00:01:40.105 --> 00:01:42.155
They're already waiting for us.

35
00:01:42.912 --> 00:01:44.268
Our ships are in position.

36
00:01:44.393 --> 00:01:47.406
and we are ready to begin
our campaign against the Geonosians.

37
00:01:47.730 --> 00:01:50.785
<i>And what about Poggle?
Any report on his location?</i>

38
00:01:50.953 --> 00:01:54.353
It seems he's holed up
at the primary droid foundry here.

39
00:01:54.707 --> 00:01:57.000
The factory is protected
by a shield generator.

40
00:01:57.125 --> 00:02:00.226
Anakin. Ki-Adi. and I shall attempt
a three-pronged attack

41
00:02:00.351 --> 00:02:03.973
through their defense lines to a
staging area just short of the shield.

42
00:02:04.098 --> 00:02:06.676
Once we have landed. we Shall
knock out the shield generator

43
00:02:07.031 --> 00:02:08.881
That is our primary target.

44
00:02:09.138 --> 00:02:13.038
<i>Isn't it risky committing three
generals to one area of the attack?</i>

45
00:02:13.875 --> 00:02:17.186
<i>If something went wrong.
we could be dealt a serious blow.</i>

46
00:02:17.354 --> 00:02:20.104
<i>To ensure that rise again
Geonosis does not.</i>

47
00:02:20.511 --> 00:02:22.161
<i>capture Poggle we must.</i>

48
00:02:22.678 --> 00:02:23.678
<i>Of course.</i>

49
00:02:24.055 --> 00:02:27.505
<i>As always. I shall leave
the strategy to you. Master Jedi.</i>

50
00:02:27.750 --> 00:02:29.365
Our thanks. Chancellor.

51
00:02:29.533 --> 00:02:31.449
<i>May the Force be with you.</i>

52
00:02:33.365 --> 00:02:34.415
Good. Cody.

53
00:02:34.731 --> 00:02:37.531
These are the coordinates
for the rendezvous.

54
00:02:37.806 --> 00:02:39.739
When we hit the ground.
we'll create a perimeter.

55
00:02:39.864 --> 00:02:42.637
Getting past their defenses here
will be the trick.

56
00:02:42.762 --> 00:02:45.599
General Mundi will come across
the defensive lines from the north.

57
00:02:45.724 --> 00:02:47.938
We will make our assault
through the middle.

58
00:02:48.063 --> 00:02:49.377
General Skywalker

59
00:02:49.502 --> 00:02:52.500
will make his attack
on the defensive lines from the south.

60
00:02:52.625 --> 00:02:56.292
And we will meet at the
rendezvous point at 0700 exactly

61
00:02:56.810 --> 00:02:58.414
If we meet with strong resistance

62
00:02:58.539 --> 00:03:00.442
and are forced down away
from the landing zone.

63
00:03:00.567 --> 00:03:04.483
hold out until we join our forces
before attacking the shield generator.

64
00:03:04.651 --> 00:03:07.111
Their front lines
are heavily fortified.

65
00:03:07.279 --> 00:03:09.697
Look at that giant wall
with all the gun emplacements.

66
00:03:10.243 --> 00:03:12.283
That won't be easy to get past.

67
00:03:12.501 --> 00:03:14.813
Don't worry.
We're not going anywhere near that.

68
00:03:14.938 --> 00:03:15.799
Come now.

69
00:03:15.924 --> 00:03:18.724
What happened to all
the enthusiasm I saw earlier?

70
00:03:18.849 --> 00:03:20.273
Don't worry about us.

71
00:03:20.398 --> 00:03:24.045
You just make sure you get yourself
to that landing zone in one piece.

72
00:03:24.337 --> 00:03:26.812
I shall be waiting for you
when you finally arrive.

73
00:03:26.937 --> 00:03:30.687
<i>Gentlemen. if you are quite finished
we have a battle to begin.</i>

74
00:03:31.252 --> 00:03:32.352
Quite right.

75
00:03:32.691 --> 00:03:35.891
Cody. prep the gunships.
I'll meet you in the hangar.

76
00:03:57.913 --> 00:04:01.299
No. sir. I wasn't involved
in the first assault on Geonosis.

77
00:04:01.424 --> 00:04:02.879
You didn't miss much.

78
00:04:03.004 --> 00:04:07.202
Last time. I was chained to a pole and
attacked by several humongous monsters.

79
00:04:07.438 --> 00:04:09.826
That sounds... entertaining.

80
00:04:10.176 --> 00:04:11.176
It was...

81
00:04:11.356 --> 00:04:12.806
for the Geonosians.

82
00:04:53.883 --> 00:04:56.033
- We all ready. Rex?
- Yes. sir.

83
00:04:56.430 --> 00:04:58.014
General Kenobi is already under way.

84
00:04:58.182 --> 00:05:00.641
He's got a head start.
We'll have to catch up.

85
00:05:04.624 --> 00:05:05.938
Good luck. General.

86
00:05:06.438 --> 00:05:08.488
There is no such thing as luck.

87
00:05:22.201 --> 00:05:24.290
Good thing those bugs can't aim.

88
00:05:44.270 --> 00:05:47.626
<i>- The flak is too heavy.
- We're down. Repeat. down.</i>

89
00:05:47.751 --> 00:05:49.101
<i>Location. five...</i>

90
00:05:49.374 --> 00:05:51.442
I just lost contact
with Skywalker's team.

91
00:05:52.125 --> 00:05:54.675
Come on. get up!
We have to keep moving.

92
00:05:58.223 --> 00:05:59.473
Here they come.

93
00:06:00.135 --> 00:06:01.285
Watch it. Watch it!

94
00:06:09.503 --> 00:06:11.654
They're falling back. Come on!

95
00:06:19.304 --> 00:06:21.138
Get the tanks on the ground now!

96
00:06:24.643 --> 00:06:26.811
Cody. get the tanks down.
Come in. Cody.

97
00:06:30.482 --> 00:06:32.682
<i>Cody. come in! Get the tanks down!</i>

98
00:06:32.944 --> 00:06:35.544
Copy that.
Pilot. begin landing sequence.

99
00:06:35.779 --> 00:06:38.072
Copy that. commander.
Have fun down there.

100
00:06:47.763 --> 00:06:49.125
Move it! Move it!

101
00:06:49.294 --> 00:06:51.147
- Here they come.
- Bugs incoming.

102
00:06:51.272 --> 00:06:52.671
Man down! Man down!

103
00:06:52.796 --> 00:06:54.922
General Kenobi. don't land.
The zone is hot.

104
00:06:56.591 --> 00:06:58.551
But there's nowhere else to go.

105
00:07:05.601 --> 00:07:07.501
We're hit. We're going down.

106
00:07:12.463 --> 00:07:13.774
Brace yourselves!

107
00:07:34.817 --> 00:07:36.338
What are our losses. captain?

108
00:07:36.635 --> 00:07:38.192
We got hit pretty hard.

109
00:07:38.317 --> 00:07:40.396
I think only Kenobi's forces
made it through the flak

110
00:07:40.521 --> 00:07:43.095
- to the landing zone.
- And what about Skywalker?

111
00:07:43.281 --> 00:07:46.352
Captain Rex reported they're still
in the middle of a firefight.

112
00:07:46.477 --> 00:07:47.877
Skywalker's tanks are gone.

113
00:07:48.002 --> 00:07:50.904
and they're trying to contact
General Kenobi's forces for support.

114
00:07:51.029 --> 00:07:53.728
In the meantime. they'll press
on to the rendezvous point.

115
00:07:53.853 --> 00:07:54.853
Very well.

116
00:07:55.348 --> 00:07:57.448
Load the injured onto the tanks.

117
00:07:57.752 --> 00:07:59.236
We'll make for that ridge.

118
00:07:59.361 --> 00:08:01.157
With any luck.
we can meet up with Skywalker

119
00:08:01.282 --> 00:08:03.382
on his way to Kenobi's position.

120
00:08:10.127 --> 00:08:13.191
- I'll speak with General Skywalker.
- Rex. what's the word?

121
00:08:13.316 --> 00:08:16.255
- Can Obi-Wan send support or not?
- I don't think so. sir.

122
00:08:16.380 --> 00:08:18.816
Cody says General Kenobi
never reached the landing site.

123
00:08:18.941 --> 00:08:21.403
- They think his gunship got shot down.
- Great.

124
00:08:21.528 --> 00:08:24.782
The one time I actually ask Obi-Wan
for help. he's nowhere to be found.

125
00:08:24.907 --> 00:08:27.139
What if something happened
to General Kenobi?

126
00:08:27.264 --> 00:08:30.139
- He could be injured or...
- No time for that kind of talk.

127
00:08:30.264 --> 00:08:33.114
We need to mobilize now.
Get the men together.

128
00:08:33.319 --> 00:08:35.272
- We're gonna rush the guns.
- Yes. sir.

129
00:08:35.768 --> 00:08:37.366
Ahsoka. you're with me.

130
00:08:37.491 --> 00:08:39.300
We need to give Rex cover
when we attack.

131
00:08:39.425 --> 00:08:41.325
Got it.
Just give the word.

132
00:08:42.213 --> 00:08:43.504
I'm worried about him too.

133
00:08:43.629 --> 00:08:45.753
But you have to keep your mind
in the here and now.

134
00:08:45.878 --> 00:08:48.494
otherwise we'll never
be able to help Obi-Wan.

135
00:08:51.040 --> 00:08:52.437
- All here. sir.
- Ready?

136
00:08:53.796 --> 00:08:55.696
Take 'em out.
Take 'em all.

137
00:09:01.884 --> 00:09:03.946
Not good.
The bugs are splitting up.

138
00:09:04.071 --> 00:09:06.645
- Boil reporting as ordered. sir.
- Waxer reporting as ordered. sir.

139
00:09:06.770 --> 00:09:09.598
We have a downed gunship 5 klicks east.
We believe it's General Kenobi's.

140
00:09:09.766 --> 00:09:12.309
I need you to get out there
and check for survivors.

141
00:09:27.875 --> 00:09:30.004
Why do we always get
the fun missions?

142
00:09:30.129 --> 00:09:31.648
Tthis isn't the fun part.

143
00:09:31.773 --> 00:09:34.473
Getting back to the square
is the fun part.

144
00:09:38.420 --> 00:09:40.114
Am I glad to see you.

145
00:09:40.239 --> 00:09:42.464
Trapper and I
are the only ones still alive.

146
00:09:42.632 --> 00:09:44.831
Good to see you. sir.
Commander Cody's established

147
00:09:44.956 --> 00:09:47.561
the square just beyond this position.
The bugs are on the move

148
00:09:47.686 --> 00:09:49.513
and trying to surround us
as we speak. sir.

149
00:09:52.767 --> 00:09:54.300
They've got the General.

150
00:09:54.425 --> 00:09:57.886
AT-TE 636.
lay down cover fire at point 3-5.

151
00:10:08.091 --> 00:10:09.991
Take it down!
Take it down!

152
00:10:16.694 --> 00:10:19.944
- Are you injured. General?
- No. nothing too serious.

153
00:10:20.184 --> 00:10:21.984
What's the situation here?

154
00:10:22.859 --> 00:10:24.136
We've got no air cover.

155
00:10:24.261 --> 00:10:26.383
two generals on the ground
beyond our position.

156
00:10:26.508 --> 00:10:28.053
and a mess of bugs surrounding us.

157
00:10:28.178 --> 00:10:30.656
The enemy was more than prepared
for our attack. sir.

158
00:10:30.781 --> 00:10:32.408
They knew our every move.

159
00:10:32.533 --> 00:10:34.874
I'm sure General Skywalker
and General Mundi

160
00:10:34.999 --> 00:10:36.518
will make it to our position.

161
00:10:36.686 --> 00:10:40.052
We just have to make sure
we're still here when they arrive.

162
00:11:02.212 --> 00:11:03.925
Negative. captain.
We will be unable

163
00:11:04.050 --> 00:11:05.804
to provide any air support
at this time.

164
00:11:06.038 --> 00:11:07.328
I understand that. sir.

165
00:11:07.453 --> 00:11:09.231
But we have 3 attack forces
on the ground

166
00:11:09.356 --> 00:11:10.928
and only one at the landing zone.

167
00:11:11.096 --> 00:11:13.740
This is a planetary-wide
invasion. captain.

168
00:11:13.865 --> 00:11:15.868
If I devote resources
to your position.

169
00:11:15.993 --> 00:11:18.811
it will mean sacrificing
other areas of the campaign.

170
00:11:18.979 --> 00:11:21.557
All we can do at this time
is help you find General Skywalker.

171
00:11:21.682 --> 00:11:22.865
All right. sir.

172
00:11:22.990 --> 00:11:25.275
I'll report to the General.
Commander jet out.

173
00:11:25.659 --> 00:11:28.209
Give me every fighter
you can scrape up.

174
00:11:28.849 --> 00:11:31.156
Have you located
General Skywalker's position?

175
00:11:31.324 --> 00:11:34.076
We think he's somewhere
along the eastern barrier.

176
00:11:34.244 --> 00:11:35.619
That's not a barrier.

177
00:11:35.994 --> 00:11:37.037
It's a fortress.

178
00:11:44.838 --> 00:11:46.438
Careful. men. careful.

179
00:11:47.962 --> 00:11:51.805
Well. this is another fine mess
you've gotten us into.

180
00:11:51.930 --> 00:11:54.358
What?
Hey. it's not my fault.

181
00:11:54.483 --> 00:11:56.531
You were supposed
to study the holomaps.

182
00:11:56.656 --> 00:11:57.656
I did!

183
00:11:58.129 --> 00:12:01.890
Remember when I reminded you
about the giant wall.

184
00:12:02.015 --> 00:12:06.048
and you said. "Don't worry. Snips.
We won't be anywhere near that. "

185
00:12:06.173 --> 00:12:08.136
Just get ready to climb.

186
00:12:09.570 --> 00:12:12.178
General. I left a squad
to protect the tanks.

187
00:12:12.303 --> 00:12:14.916
Are you sure this is the
shortest way to the landing zone?

188
00:12:15.041 --> 00:12:16.925
No. I'm not sure. commander.

189
00:12:17.050 --> 00:12:19.350
All I can do is trust my instincts.

190
00:12:33.178 --> 00:12:35.929
Wait a minute. wait a minute.
I have a wing vibration up ahead.

191
00:12:56.669 --> 00:13:00.317
Don't stop. We must push on.
Forward!

192
00:13:01.687 --> 00:13:04.563
- So what's the plan. General?
- Just keep us covered. Rex.

193
00:13:04.688 --> 00:13:07.192
There's too much laser fire
for all of us to make the climb.

194
00:13:07.317 --> 00:13:08.831
Ahsoka and I will handle this.

195
00:13:08.956 --> 00:13:10.964
Just be ready
when that wall comes down.

196
00:13:58.555 --> 00:14:00.693
How many droids
have you shot down so far?

197
00:14:00.818 --> 00:14:03.568
- 25.
- You're falling behind.

198
00:14:04.003 --> 00:14:04.819
Let's go.

199
00:14:21.911 --> 00:14:24.611
Focus on the droids
on the top of the wall.

200
00:14:31.383 --> 00:14:32.270
Man down!

201
00:15:01.282 --> 00:15:02.412
Look for a hatch.

202
00:15:02.537 --> 00:15:05.037
We need to put the explosives
inside the wall.

203
00:15:06.350 --> 00:15:07.177
Found one.

204
00:15:32.486 --> 00:15:33.940
- Did you get them?
- Catch.

205
00:15:37.811 --> 00:15:38.904
Come on. Rex.

206
00:15:39.072 --> 00:15:40.172
Up and away.

207
00:15:46.207 --> 00:15:47.207
Help!

208
00:16:08.852 --> 00:16:10.952
Next time. just tell me to jump.

209
00:16:11.197 --> 00:16:13.147
Now. where's the fun in that?

210
00:16:13.481 --> 00:16:15.537
Come on. we can't keep
Obi-Wan waiting.

211
00:16:15.662 --> 00:16:17.712
You heard him. lads.
Let's go!

212
00:16:27.620 --> 00:16:30.414
We're almost through.
Bring in the flame throwers.

213
00:16:40.925 --> 00:16:42.325
Look. what's that?

214
00:16:51.352 --> 00:16:53.186
Master Mundi. do you read me?

215
00:16:53.354 --> 00:16:56.074
We are here. Skywalker.
We took a slight detour

216
00:16:56.199 --> 00:16:58.172
that put us out of communications
for a bit.

217
00:16:58.297 --> 00:17:00.439
This has been
a day for detours. Master.

218
00:17:00.564 --> 00:17:04.214
Indeed. But now the road is clear.
I can see the landing zone.

219
00:17:04.977 --> 00:17:06.491
It does not look good.

220
00:17:07.262 --> 00:17:08.952
Can you get me Admiral Yularen?

221
00:17:12.824 --> 00:17:14.595
<i>Admiral. we're
at the breaking point.</i>

222
00:17:14.720 --> 00:17:16.586
<i>You've got to get
some fighters down here.</i>

223
00:17:16.711 --> 00:17:20.561
You are in luck. General Skywalker.
I have one squadron available.

224
00:17:28.852 --> 00:17:31.241
Retreat!
Go. go. go. go!

225
00:17:40.363 --> 00:17:42.863
Every shot counts!
Give it all you got!

226
00:17:44.825 --> 00:17:46.031
Reinforcements!

227
00:17:46.199 --> 00:17:48.299
The reinforcements have arrived!

228
00:17:57.068 --> 00:17:58.470
Go. go. go. go!

229
00:17:58.942 --> 00:18:00.292
Move it! Move it!

230
00:18:00.417 --> 00:18:03.517
- You heard him. lads. let's go!
- Up to the front!

231
00:18:04.092 --> 00:18:06.002
- Come on!
- Hurry. hurry!

232
00:18:06.247 --> 00:18:08.647
- There they are.
- Move it. move it!

233
00:18:10.390 --> 00:18:11.592
Master Kenobi.

234
00:18:13.309 --> 00:18:14.859
What happened to you?

235
00:18:15.395 --> 00:18:17.585
I might ask you the same question.

236
00:18:17.710 --> 00:18:21.233
Our combined forces should be enough
to destroy the shield generator.

237
00:18:21.401 --> 00:18:24.653
Anakin. you'll need to take
a small squad through the shield.

238
00:18:24.821 --> 00:18:27.593
as close as you can get
to their gun emplacements.

239
00:18:27.718 --> 00:18:28.575
From there.

240
00:18:28.700 --> 00:18:30.791
you'll be able to temporarily jam
their scanners

241
00:18:30.916 --> 00:18:33.745
so they are unable to target
the incoming tanks.

242
00:18:33.913 --> 00:18:35.857
Once the tanks knock out the shield.

243
00:18:35.982 --> 00:18:39.209
Master Mundi can bring the rest
of the troops in with the gunships.

244
00:18:40.102 --> 00:18:41.721
Consider it done. Master.

245
00:18:48.960 --> 00:18:51.010
All units are in position. sir.

246
00:18:52.021 --> 00:18:54.271
Tell Skywalker to start the attack.

247
00:18:54.559 --> 00:18:55.909
Begin the attack.

248
00:19:35.718 --> 00:19:38.568
Let's jam their scanners.
Droid poppers ready.

249
00:19:45.514 --> 00:19:46.959
Looks like it's working.

250
00:19:47.084 --> 00:19:49.584
It won't last long.
Bring up the tanks.

251
00:20:31.887 --> 00:20:34.157
So. Master. what was your total?

252
00:20:35.127 --> 00:20:36.414
Not now. Ahsoka.

253
00:20:36.539 --> 00:20:39.616
Come on. Are you afraid
you lost this time?

254
00:20:39.959 --> 00:20:42.804
Fine. 55. that's my count.
And you?

255
00:20:44.906 --> 00:20:45.752
60.

256
00:20:46.036 --> 00:20:47.386
Looks like I won.

257
00:20:48.739 --> 00:20:51.681
Yeah. but I called in
the air strike. Tie.

258
00:20:52.426 --> 00:20:53.826
You're impossible.

259
00:20:54.554 --> 00:20:57.180
I'll never understand
how you can simplify these battles

260
00:20:57.305 --> 00:20:58.955
into some kind of game.

261
00:21:02.142 --> 00:21:05.074
Take care of yourselves.
I expect to see both of you back here

262
00:21:05.199 --> 00:21:07.399
by the time I've destroyed
the main factory.

263
00:21:07.567 --> 00:21:09.097
We shall do our best.

264
00:21:09.222 --> 00:21:10.777
65. Skywalker.

265
00:21:11.320 --> 00:21:12.570
- I'm sorry?

266
00:21:12.738 --> 00:21:14.489
My total. 65.

267
00:21:15.547 --> 00:21:16.899
So what do I win?

268
00:21:21.872 --> 00:21:24.272
My everlasting respect.
Master Mundi.

269
00:21:25.669 --> 00:21:28.069
That is a gift
Anakin rarely bestows.

270
00:21:28.921 --> 00:21:30.071
I assure you.
